      <title>隨著 Concord 提高對夏奇拉音樂所有者的報價，Hipgnosis 的競購戰愈演愈烈</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/hipgnosis-bidding-war-intensifies-concord-hikes-offer-shakira-music-owner-2024-04-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[週四，Hipgnosis Songs Fund 的股價上漲，此前阿波羅支持的Concord 出價超過了私募股權巨頭Blackstone 的報價，為夏奇拉(Shakira) 和金發女郎(Blondie) 等藝術家的音樂版權所有者發起了一場競購戰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/hipgnosis-bidding-war-intensifies-concord-hikes-offer-shakira-music-owner-2024-04-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 07:49:30 GMT</pubDate>
