      <title>阿斯特捷利康突破第一季預期後實現飛躍</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-beats-first-quarter-revenue-profit-estimates-2024-04-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[週四，在對其重磅藥物的需求和合作藥品穩定銷售的推動下，阿斯特捷利康的季度收入和利潤超出了市場預期，並導致其股價上漲超過 5%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-beats-first-quarter-revenue-profit-estimates-2024-04-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 06:06:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
