      <title>受國內銷售疲軟影響，現代汽車第一季獲利下降2.4%</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/hyundai-motors-q1-profit-drops-24-beats-forecasts-2024-04-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韓國汽車製造商現代汽車公司第一季利潤下降 2.4%，受到國內銷量下滑的影響，並警告稱，由於競爭加劇和全球經濟狀況的不確定性，業務前景充滿挑戰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/hyundai-motors-q1-profit-drops-24-beats-forecasts-2024-04-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 05:04:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>LG Display因淡季需求下降而重回季度虧損</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/lg-display-returns-quarterly-loss-drop-off-season-demand-2024-04-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韓國平板製造商 LG Display 在第一季再次出現營運虧損，原因是電視大型顯示面板和智慧型手機小型面板的需求疲軟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/lg-display-returns-quarterly-loss-drop-off-season-demand-2024-04-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 04:51:15 GMT</pubDate>
